{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act47side", "eventName": "未許之地", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "UR-3", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "跌落保護", "storyInfo": "得到高登幫助的“幸運瘤獸”得以留在園區，但斯凱敏銳地從他們的設施中察覺到了異常。另一邊，逃跑的兩人被追兵意外炸進了高登的秘密收藏室——這裡藏著高登用來幫助“幸運瘤獸”和其他許多企業的違禁走私品。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g5_floatingstation", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loading_intro", "key": "$loading_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#4$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#4$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "優勝劣汰，園區準則……萊茵什麼時候也被歸到淘汰者的隊伍裡了？", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#4$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#1$1", "posfrom": "300,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#4$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-60,0", "duration": 0.4, "focus": "m", "isblock": "false"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "60,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉……呃，斯凱先生？你怎麼在這裡！", "name": "雅斯彭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2041_1#4$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這話應該我來問吧？“幸運瘤獸”應該已經辦完進駐資格註銷手續了，你在這裡幹嘛？", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有利用任何非法手段！在註銷進駐資格前，我們靠自己解決了技術難題，實在太幸運了……", "name": "雅斯彭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2041_1#4$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "解決了？為什麼沒有人回報工程部？", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可能是事出突然，交接上出了問題……", "name": "雅斯彭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2041_1#5$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再、再說了，剛剛高登長官都在廣播裡宣布了——萊茵生命主導的工程檢修全面暫停。", "name": "雅斯彭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2041_1#5$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，我也不需要向你彙報了吧？", "name": "雅斯彭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2041_1#3$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#1$1", "posfrom": "70,0", "posto": "-30,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三天都沒辦法解決的問題，突然就搞定了？", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幸運的“幸運瘤獸”嗎……", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g6_floatinglabmodule", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快點，讀數，快點！他們的人說不定什麼時候就回來了……", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……數據完全達標。不如說達標得有點太精準了，簡直像是對著標準刻意調整過一樣。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？這幾個……不是園區通用的螺絲型號吧？", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "轉不動。完全焊住了……整個核心動力裝置都被封死了。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_energywell", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "en"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.5, "channel": "en", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……但我聽也能聽出來，園區允許使用的動力元件裡，沒有任何一個型號能發出這種聲響。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#8$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "en"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們是從哪裡搞來的這種不符合規定的奇怪元件？園區所有零件的採購權不是都歸——", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵……原來是這樣，我還以為園區的準則真的是優勝劣汰。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_makephonecall"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telephonebusy"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……忙著幫那個混蛋整理萊茵的事故報告嗎？", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，就算上報給娜斯提主任，她也會質疑我沒有證據。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有誰能幫我……", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g9_headquarter", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 3.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 1.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_249_muesys_1#1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的車還有五分鐘到。要是實驗園區有吉祥物玩偶，我會幫你帶一個。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_249_muesys_1#4", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我才不是需要人哄的小孩子。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "char_249_muesys_1#4"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那再見？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_249_muesys_1#5", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你從塞雷婭辦公室出來之後，就一直待在走廊裡跟你的“樹枝”玩拋接球。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "char_249_muesys_1#5"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_249_muesys_1#4", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "故意拖延時間不見我？我都看到了哦。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "char_249_muesys_1#4"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "利用水分身侵犯個人隱私應當被追究法律責任。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_249_muesys_1#5", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在哥倫比亞出現第二個水精靈之前，你無處申訴。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "char_249_muesys_1#5"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_swordwhoosh", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話音剛落，娜斯提腰間的“樹枝”突然向上伸長了一截，枝端對準水精靈的方向，旋開工具片。"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_muesys_hide", "layer": 4.0, "roy": 79.0, "roz": 100.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_watersubbreak", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#11$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "80,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.3, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繆爾賽思像排練了無數次一般朝右移了一步，躲開仿生樹枝機器人的惡作劇。"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_249_muesys_1#4", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_249_muesys_1#4", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真過分，你明知道我現在在謝拉格，不可能親自來送行。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "char_249_muesys_1#4"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠距離維持水分身對你的消耗不小，這麼擔心我搞砸克麗斯騰的遺產？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_249_muesys_1#7", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我擔心的不是萬星園後續計劃的實驗進度，而是你。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "char_249_muesys_1#7"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_249_muesys_1#7", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "種子長成樹苗尚且需要時間，更何況你希望它能長成參天巨木。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "char_249_muesys_1#7"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_249_muesys_1#5", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放輕鬆點，連斐爾迪南都不會對你目前的成果挑三揀四。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "char_249_muesys_1#5"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是因為我封鎖了他的信箱地址。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_249_muesys_1#2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳……", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "char_249_muesys_1#2"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_249_muesys_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在特里蒙郊外的地下，你偷偷幫克麗斯騰實現她的夢想，現在終於輪到你自己了。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "char_249_muesys_1#1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_249_muesys_1#7", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜斯提，你有沒有想過……", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "char_249_muesys_1#7"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會回河谷。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "河谷的安寧不屬於一個殘缺的女妖，也無法為她帶來靈感。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_249_muesys_1#4", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是……", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "char_249_muesys_1#4"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_carhorn", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我該走了。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "char_249_muesys_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等一下，給你。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "char_249_muesys_1#1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盆栽？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#6$1"}, {"id": 167,